  "definitions": {
    "b-label": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 6,
      "text": "TAXONOMY",
      "align": "left",
      "width": "hug",
      "height": "hug"
    },
    "b-confirm": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Confirmshaming\n\nLabelling the decline option with loaded language: \"No thanks, I don't want to save money.\"\n\n**Mechanism:** Shame as friction.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "b-roach": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Roach Motel\n\nEasy to sign up; impossible to cancel. Cancellation buried behind calls, waiting periods, or multi-step forms.\n\n**Mechanism:** Asymmetric friction.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "b-trick": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Trick Questions\n\nDouble-negative opt-outs, pre-checked boxes, ambiguous checkbox labels.\n\n**Mechanism:** Cognitive load exploited to produce false consent.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "b-misdirect": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Misdirection\n\nVisual hierarchy steers attention toward a profitable option while obscuring the alternative.\n\n**Mechanism:** Preattentive salience exploited.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "b-hidden": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Hidden Costs\n\nCharges added at final checkout step after the user has committed time and decision energy to the purchase.\n\n**Mechanism:** Sunk cost exploitation.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "b-scarcity": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### False Scarcity\n\n\"Only 2 left!\" or countdown timers that reset. Fabricated urgency or scarcity to pressure immediate decisions.\n\n**Mechanism:** Loss aversion activated artificially.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "b-disgust": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Disguised Ads\n\nSponsored content designed to look like editorial; download buttons camouflaged as UI chrome.\n\n**Mechanism:** Trust transferred from trusted context to commercial.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "b-social": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Social Proof Manipulation\n\nFabricated reviews, inflated user counts, or real-time activity notifications that exaggerate demand.\n\n**Mechanism:** Social proof heuristic exploited.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "b-forced": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Forced Continuity\n\nFree trial ends, paid subscription begins automatically. Notification is buried or absent.\n\n**Mechanism:** Inertia and notification blindness exploited.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    }
  },
